<header>
<h1>Alláh-u-Abhá — Dear friends and neighbours,</h1>
<p class="kicker">Welcome to a simple pānui-style page for the Hamilton West campaign. Plain words. Clear costs. Do the basics well.</p>
</header>

<!-- Nav -->
